{"id":8768,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>　　《炎黄春秋》<SPAN lang=EN-US>2012</SPAN>年第<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>期吴琦幸文《王元化：对启蒙思想的反思》第<SPAN lang=EN-US>14</SPAN>页中“……好像高尔基在<SPAN lang=EN-US>1939</SPAN>年也有过这样的想法”明显有误，因为高尔基早在<SPAN lang=EN-US>1936</SPAN>年就辞世了。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 242.45pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 23.0\" class=MsoNormal><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">武汉读者　胡水清</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></B></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\"><FONT size=3>《炎黄春秋》<SPAN lang=EN-US>2012</SPAN>年第<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>期《<SPAN lang=EN-US>1973</SPAN>年周恩来为何挨批》一文中“周恩来陪同毛泽东会见赞比亚总统卡翁达后”（第<SPAN lang=EN-US>70</SPAN>页）中的“后”字应改为“时”；第<SPAN lang=EN-US>75</SPAN>页右栏倒数第<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>行“邢从周”有误，应为“邢宗周”<SPAN lang=EN-US>;</SPAN>第<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>期第<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>页中“南美洲共产党执政的国家只有古巴”有误，应为“美州共产党执政的国家只有古巴”。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 274.05pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 26.0\" class=MsoNormal><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3>本刊编辑部</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>","title":"勘误","time":1333975537999}